  "subject": "Remove Hazelcast from NCMP Module Sync",
  "commit_message": "Remove Hazelcast from NCMP Module Sync\n\n- Remove shared moduleSyncWorkQueue: new algorithm is that\n  each instance has it's own shuffled queue.\n- Remove locking mechanism, as it doesn't work reliably and\n  is not needed after removing moduleSyncWorkQueue.\n- moduleSyncStartedOnCmHandles is kept for now.\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2161\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: If8b5bf64c80eabea47afdb00ac45571190be406d\n",
